# Google Custom Search API (for item image search)
# 1. Create a Programmable Search Engine at https://programmablesearchengine.google.com/
# 2. Enable "Image search" and "Search the entire web" in the engine settings
# 3. Copy the Search Engine ID
# 4. Create an API key at https://console.cloud.google.com/apis/credentials
# 5. Enable the "Custom Search API" at https://console.cloud.google.com/apis/library/customsearch.googleapis.com
VITE_GOOGLE_CSE_API_KEY=
VITE_GOOGLE_CSE_ID=
